Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOYS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此為天選之人孕育於心中的奇跡之花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人開出聖潔的花朵 也有人開出有毒的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大偵探時代爭奇鬥艷的兩朵花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為偵探與怪盜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.01,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本字幕由天使字幕組製作 僅功學習交流之用\N翻譯:無盡的旅行者 旭日無光\N　TV後期:依戀緋鞠　BD後期:殘月止水\N　技術指導:小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田園被…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到黎明了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從這裡出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反省會已經完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是睡一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠不足可是肌膚的大敵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須馬上趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學生們還在等著我去做熱騰騰的早餐!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah beautiful 越獄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的越獄就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫作「脫了然後獄」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.51,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[越獄的日文是「脫獄」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:58.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[美味的壽司]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:58.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[尼羅河慘案]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:58.40,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[尼羅河慘案:（Death on the  Nile）\N1978年根據阿加莎·克里斯蒂在1937年出版的同名小說改編的一部英國電影。]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的橫濱外匯交易市場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開盤價95.88日元 95日元…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的田園被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡… 好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰幹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,農場被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃啊… 好吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼能痛下殺手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該這麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 好吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 吃飽了吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 手上黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借用下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 是木村先生的點播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黃瓜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有黃瓜殘留在田園裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～ 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 魚糕 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種很懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,農場被摧毀就是她們最大的痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利埃特大人今天也心情不好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在不爽福爾摩斯小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們一定要親手去擊潰她們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來肯定會心情變好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利埃特大人會對我們綻放出她那女神般美麗的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 只是想像一下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就很煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高漲!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高漲!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情緒高漲!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來 總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走! 大家一起去打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮洛 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 再次拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:44.69,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}[背上的字:又來了啊]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮮花 漂亮的鮮花(原曲是Sara Montiel的La Violetera)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:48.16,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[後面三個小孩原型為(西岸良平:永遠的三丁目的夕陽)、\n(蠟筆小新:小新+阿呆)、(平成教育委員會:勉強小僧)、(COUNT DOWN TV:菊池) ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.03,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[超橫濱美大]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好模特兒啊 艾露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膨脹的東西爆發了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要畫了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.67,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[絕對賺錢的炒外匯術]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對柯蒂利亞本來就沒期待著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但夏洛跟艾莉的工錢匯過來後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全部投到希臘的國債上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊 只要兩個月就能蓋房子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾露 妳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是美妙的素材呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我本人送妳的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…給我?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.03,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[港口看得清楚到困惑之丘公園 展望台:原型為「能看到港口的公園」， 「看得清楚到困惑」出自60年代的電視廣告「大量天線」的廣告詞]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了熬過的雞骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去全力賣花了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當模特兒挺累的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮洛如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦啊 當然也努力的打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到我這種等級 做了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是充滿夢想的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫家切利畫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的素描
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.77,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[原型好像是岡本太郎的作品「にらめっこ」+「午後の日」+「太陽の塔」的綜合體]）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這裡是眼睛 這個是鼻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼 這裡是嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 讓他預付工資啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅畫能送給我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像我很久以前生離死別的初戀啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是80年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80年?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她名叫日笠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.23,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[原型為阿加莎克里斯蒂 赫爾克林伯頓是其筆下的偵探]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日笠克里斯蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日笠她很害羞 一直都帶著面具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是帶著那個面具!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 就像小衣衣一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日笠是個很溫柔的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還有後續
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老年人的話都很長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 我爺爺的話也很長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說拯救受傷的仙鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.18,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[日本的民間故事]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至為在暴風中擱淺的鯨魚治療
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯨魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢的話 我多的都快發霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個決定命運的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去看橫濱王族的墳墓─胡夫濱法老的金字塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:44.51,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[原型為埃及最大的金字塔─古夫(胡夫)金字塔]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美麗的金字塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳更加地美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後日笠小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:08:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時開始 就再也沒見過面了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼去找 都再也沒有見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼找都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼一直孤身一人迎來了白壽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.01,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[白壽:99歲的雅稱 因「百」字去一 故稱]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一枚照片都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少讓我剩下的時日能跟那幅畫一起度過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會免費送給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是花了相當多的錢弄到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花什麼錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫讓崎妮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓給的讓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我是很仁慈的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 讓給你也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.18,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[屬名為福爾摩斯的作者:亞瑟·柯南·道爾]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1…1千萬!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:50.11,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[原型是「怪～ayakashi～」主角]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒童支票?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啊 紙條而已紙條而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說只是紙條而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這個說不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真想要這幅畫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上點壽司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高級壽司100…不 1000個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千個壽司!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 夏洛 大家 有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老闆 我是道爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.30,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[道爾:drill 尼羅河慘案中的角色名，也是福爾摩斯的作者名]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用橫濱灣現釣的新鮮魚做成高級壽司1000個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急送到港口看得清楚到困惑之丘公園來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也附上鮭魚冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:44.58,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[日本第一家冰淇淋店在橫濱開幕]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擅長談判的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呀 妮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 等下 壽司!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日笠!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.26,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[地板上:吃]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.01,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[壽司店老闆的造型類似于「根性青蛙」里的梅先生]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到 我看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力工作 去賺女兒的手術費
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親一人養育著年幼的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但女兒得了病需要999萬元的手術費所以拼命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待治好女兒的病之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人想盡情馳騁於清爽微風吹拂的草原之上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司屋的老闆捏出的壽司真是絕品呀～～～!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說很想很想吃到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆也真辛苦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂利亞…剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去了 要出公園了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮洛 夏洛 還有柯蒂利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽下…我的話…聽一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:12:00.03,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[巡音luka+花枝娘]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家的壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日笠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.41,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[外交官牌照]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 這裡是my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪同她生產promise
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是堵上未來我也必須要到達!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh NO 剎車失靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My God
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千萬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come on come on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO 停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.82,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[拉麵屋原型為中華一番]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:13:04.13,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[貓 幼兒 主婦是「海螺小姐サザエさん 」中的角色]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:03.47,PS,,0000,0000,0000,,[宮崎駿大師]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOOOOOOOO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My God
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交官from home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.69,PS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[ET的GO HOME的neta]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛 妮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是TO TOY TOY…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重要的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在壽司屋 我努力工作著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 道爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高級壽司一千個 多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是通報裡說帶著福爾摩斯小隊笨蛋們暴走的車?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外交官牌照 管轄外的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在車架上載人也無法問罪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白跑了一趟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為能把那群大笨蛋以違反道路交通法的罪名打入大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖 my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力了 good job
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨晚的暴風雨而擱淺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身體下面的畫是很重要的東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道星星很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 讓一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了壽司 為了道爾爺爺的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 女兒情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福 情況很安定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日笠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳怎麼知道的這件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了壽司跟爺爺的黃泉禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要那幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一動也不動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOY…S
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是怪盜帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚一定要讓妳們下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打妳們屁股哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了亞森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 我心愛的日笠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:57.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\NTOYS…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就能吃壽司了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壽司是指這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的田園被鏟除了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的打擊恢復了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將 最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我向女兒問聲好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有在聽嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉也快來吃 不然要吃完了哦
