Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 福爾摩斯偵探學院要廢校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢校?
