Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOYS恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOY…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOYS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此為天選之人孕育於心中的奇跡之花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人開出聖潔的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人開出有毒的花朵
